    Set Environment Variable  TEST_ESX_BUILD  ${esx_build}
    Set Environment Variable  TEST_VCSA_BUILD  ${vc_build}
    Set Environment Variable  TEST_OS  ${os}

    Log To Console  ${\n}........................................
